yingyinNormal.en: Please hold all questions till the end of the presentation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请等演讲结束后再提问。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, very nice presentation. I'd like to see this shrink ray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这提议真给力，我想看看这缩小射线

yingyinNormal.en: Oh no, wait a minute, wait, I've got a presentation tomorrow. I can't miss that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，差点忘了，我明天有个报告，不能缺席。

yingyinNormal.en: First of all, that was a terrific presentation. Terrific. I know the General. We should take this to him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，你的演示很精彩，非常完美，我认识将军，我们应该向他汇报。

yingyinNormal.en: So, you know, isn't there maybe some way you and Sheldon could compromise on this whole presentation thing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你跟谢尔顿在演讲这件事情上就没有互相妥协的余地吗？

yingyinNormal.en: It's actually not bad. But my true purpose in being here will be revealed in this brief PowerPoint presentation. Lights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还真不赖嘛。但我来此的真正目的是来做一个简要的幻灯片演说。关灯。

yingyinNormal.en: There's something off with your presentation, Private. Can't place it. Is it your hair? Is it the wrinkle in your trousers?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的表演有失常态，列兵。很难说。是你的头发？还是你裤子上的皱纹？

yingyinNormal.en: Why Sheldon Cooper, PhD, should go to Switzerland to see the CERN super collider: a PowerPoint presentation by Sheldon Cooper, PhD. Oh, for God's sake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么谢尔顿·库珀博士必须去瑞士欧核中心参观超级对撞机的理由，发言人：谢尔顿·库珀博士。我的老天爷。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't really expect you to believe me, given that all you could think about during my presentation was what sort of pie they were serving in the commissary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不指望你相信我，因为在我发言的时候，所有你能想到的只是小卖部里卖什么样的馅饼。
